channel.title: ⌠Runescape Renders⌡
channel.description:
[center]This thread is intended to be a place to post your Runescape related Renders so others may use them. All Renders must be [b][u]MADE BY YOU[/u][/b] or they wont be added to the main post. They should also be decent quality. You will be given credit by your name being added next to the render that you contribute.[/center]
Please use this format while posting your renders: (image) What this is a render of your name ___________________________________________________
So it would look like this: [img]http://img694.imageshack.us/img694/549/minigame.png[/img] Minigame logo Weasey
I'll be contributing to this also, so I will start it off.
[img]http://img192.imageshack.us/img192/5875/cls.png[/img] CLS in inventory Weasey
Begin posting your renders!
